---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Best Korean BBQ Restaurants in Singapore" description="We ate our way through 15 KBBQ joints across the island so you don't have to.">

  <!-- ===== HERO IMAGE + OVERLAY ===== -->
  <div class="article-hero">
    <div class="hero-bg" style="background: linear-gradient(145deg, #d4a574 0%, #8b6548 50%, #5a4030 100%);"></div>
    <div class="hero-overlay">
      <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href="/eat/">Eat</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; Review</div>
      <div class="pillar-tag">EAT &middot; REVIEW</div>
      <h1>Best Korean BBQ Restaurants in Singapore: A Definitive Guide</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">We ate our way through 15 KBBQ joints across the island so you don't have to. Here's who made the cut — and who didn't.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ===== META BAR (author, date, share) ===== -->
  <div class="article-meta-bar">
    <div class="meta-left">
      <span>By Eric</span>
      <span>25 March 2026</span>
      <span>8 min read</span>
    </div>
    <div class="share-icons">
      <span class="share-label">Share</span>
      <a href="#" class="share-btn" data-share="copy" title="Copy link">&#128279;</a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/" class="share-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="Instagram">IG</a>
      <a href="#" class="share-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="Facebook">f</a>
      <a href="#" class="share-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="WhatsApp">&#9742;</a>
      <a href="#" class="share-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="Threads">&#129525;</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ===== ARTICLE BODY + SIDEBAR ===== -->
  <div class="article-layout">
    <article class="article-body">

      <!-- IG Video Embed -->
      <div class="ig-embed">
        <div class="ig-placeholder">IG VIDEO EMBED</div>
        <div class="ig-label">@thehansang.sg &middot; Instagram</div>
      </div>

      <div class="info-card">
        <h3>Quick Take</h3>
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-item"><div class="info-label">Rating</div><div class="info-value">8.5 / 10</div></div>
          <div class="info-item"><div class="info-label">Price Range</div><div class="info-value">$$</div></div>
          <div class="info-item"><div class="info-label">Best Dish</div><div class="info-value">Chadol Baegi</div></div>
          <div class="info-item"><div class="info-label">Skip This</div><div class="info-value">Bulgogi</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>Korean BBQ in Singapore has exploded over the past few years. What was once a niche dining experience found only in Tanjong Pagar has spread across the island — from Jurong East to Tampines, Beauty World to Novena.</p>

      <h2>What Makes Great Korean BBQ?</h2>

      <p>It's not just about the meat. The best Korean BBQ joints get everything right: the quality of the banchan, the ventilation system, the grill type (charcoal versus gas), and of course, the marination.</p>

      <p>We visited 15 restaurants over three months, spending an average of $45 per person per visit. Each restaurant was scored on meat quality, banchan variety, ambiance, value for money, and overall experience.</p>

      <blockquote>The difference between a good Korean BBQ and a great one is in the details — the sesame oil, the quality of the lettuce wraps, the attentiveness of the staff.</blockquote>

      <h2>Our Top 5 Picks</h2>

      <h3>1. Placeholder Restaurant 1 — Tanjong Pagar</h3>
      <p>Still the gold standard after all these years. The charcoal grill gives everything that smoky depth you can't get from gas. Their chadol baegi melts on the tongue, and the banchan spread is generous.</p>

      <h3>2. Placeholder Restaurant 2 — Beauty World</h3>
      <p>A hidden gem near Beauty World MRT. Small space, but the quality punches well above its weight. The pork belly here is pre-marinated with a garlic-soy base that caramelises beautifully.</p>

      <div class="info-card restaurant-info">
        <h3>Restaurant Info</h3>
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-item"><div class="info-label">Address</div><div class="info-value">45 Somerset Walk</div></div>
          <div class="info-item"><div class="info-label">MRT</div><div class="info-value">Tanjong Pagar</div></div>
          <div class="info-item"><div class="info-label">Hours</div><div class="info-value">11am - 10pm</div></div>
          <div class="info-item"><div class="info-label">Price Range</div><div class="info-value">$$ per person</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="article-tags">
        <div class="tags-label">Tags</div>
        <div class="tags-list">
          <a href="/eat/" class="tag">KBBQ</a>
          <a href="/eat/" class="tag">Reviews</a>
          <a href="/eat/" class="tag">Tanjong Pagar</a>
          <a href="/eat/" class="tag">Korean BBQ</a>
          <a href="/eat/" class="tag">Singapore</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </article>

    <!-- ===== SIDEBAR ===== -->
    <aside class="article-sidebar">
      <div class="sidebar-section">
        <h4>Recommendations</h4>
        <div class="rec-card">
          <div class="rec-img"><div class="img-placeholder" style="width:100%;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(145deg,#c4b8a8,#a89888);"></div></div>
          <div class="rec-tag">EAT &middot; REVIEW</div>
          <h5>Where to Find the Best Jjigae in Singapore</h5>
          <div class="card-meta">18 March 2026</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rec-card">
          <div class="rec-img"><div class="img-placeholder" style="width:100%;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(145deg,#b8a898,#9a8878);"></div></div>
          <div class="rec-tag">EAT &middot; GUIDE</div>
          <h5>Korean Fried Chicken: Ultimate Guide</h5>
          <div class="card-meta">12 March 2026</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sidebar-section">
        <h4>Most Read</h4>
        <div class="rec-card">
          <div class="rec-tag">COOK &middot; RECIPE</div>
          <h5>Golden Ratio Noodle Sauce</h5>
          <div class="card-meta">11 October 2025</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rec-card">
          <div class="rec-tag">EAT &middot; REVIEW</div>
          <h5>Placeholder Restaurant: Is It Worth It?</h5>
          <div class="card-meta">8 March 2026</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>

  <!-- ===== MORE FROM THE HANSANG ===== -->
  <div class="more-articles">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h3>More from The Hansang</h3>
      <a href="/eat/">View All</a>
    </div>
    <div class="more-grid">
      <div class="more-card">
        <div class="more-img"><div class="img-placeholder" style="width:100%;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(145deg,#c8b8a0,#a89878);"></div></div>
        <div class="more-tag">EAT &middot; GUIDE</div>
        <h4>Best Korean Restaurants Near Tanjong Pagar</h4>
        <div class="card-meta">20 March 2026</div>
      </div>
      <div class="more-card">
        <div class="more-img"><div class="img-placeholder" style="width:100%;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(145deg,#d8c8b0,#b89878);"></div></div>
        <div class="more-tag">COOK &middot; RECIPE</div>
        <h4>Korean Cream Cheese Garlic Bread</h4>
        <div class="card-meta">18 October 2025</div>
      </div>
      <div class="more-card">
        <div class="more-img"><div class="img-placeholder" style="width:100%;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(145deg,#a89080,#887060);"></div></div>
        <div class="more-tag">EAT &middot; REVIEW</div>
        <h4>Placeholder: Worth the Hype?</h4>
        <div class="card-meta">15 March 2026</div>
      </div>
      <div class="more-card">
        <div class="more-img"><div class="img-placeholder" style="width:100%;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(145deg,#b8a090,#988070);"></div></div>
        <div class="more-tag">COOK &middot; RECIPE</div>
        <h4>Perfect Tteokbokki at Home</h4>
        <div class="card-meta">10 March 2026</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ===== HERO IMAGE WITH OVERLAY ===== */
  .article-hero {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    height: 480px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .article-hero .hero-bg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, #d4a574 0%, #8b6548 50%, #5a4030 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .article-hero .hero-overlay {
    position: absolute; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    padding: 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.7) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.3) 60%, transparent 100%);
  }
  .hero-overlay .breadcrumb {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .hero-overlay .breadcrumb a {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .hero-overlay .breadcrumb a:hover { color: #fff; }
  .hero-overlay .pillar-tag {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #B8432A;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .hero-overlay h1 {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    max-width: 700px;
  }
  .hero-overlay .subtitle {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  /* ===== ARTICLE META BAR ===== */
  .article-meta-bar {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px 40px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
  }
  .meta-left {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #999;
  }
  .meta-left span { margin-right: 16px; }

  /* Share icons */
  .share-icons {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .share-icons .share-label {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #999;
    margin-right: 8px;
  }
  .share-btn {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #666;
    font-size: 13px;
    background: none;
  }
  .share-btn:hover { border-color: #1C1714; background: #f8f8f8; }

  /* ===== ARTICLE BODY + SIDEBAR ===== */
  .article-layout {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 40px 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
    gap: 48px;
  }

  /* Main article body */
  .article-body {
    max-width: 660px;
  }
  .article-body p {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .article-body h2 {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1C1714;
    margin: 40px 0 16px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .article-body h3 {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1C1714;
    margin: 32px 0 12px;
  }
  .article-body blockquote {
    border-left: 3px solid #B8432A;
    padding: 4px 0 4px 24px;
    margin: 32px 0;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #666;
  }

  /* IG Video Embed placeholder */
  .ig-embed {
    background: #fafafa;
    border: 1px solid #eee;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 24px;
    margin: 32px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .ig-embed .ig-placeholder {
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, #2a2420, #1C1714);
    border-radius: 6px;
    height: 400px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .ig-embed .ig-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #999;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* Info card (Quick Take for reviews, Recipe Card for recipes) */
  .info-card {
    background: #fafafa;
    border: 1px solid #eee;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 28px;
    margin: 32px 0;
  }
  .info-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #1C1714;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
  }
  .info-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .info-item .info-label {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .info-item .info-value {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1C1714;
  }

  /* Body image */
  .body-image {
    margin: 32px 0;
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .body-image .img-placeholder {
    height: 360px;
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, #c4b8a8, #a89888);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .body-image figcaption {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #999;
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ===== TAGS ===== */
  .article-tags {
    margin: 40px 0;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 2px solid #eee;
  }
  .article-tags .tags-label {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .tags-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .tag {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: #666;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 20px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  .tag:hover { border-color: #B8432A; color: #B8432A; }

  /* ===== SIDEBAR ===== */
  .article-sidebar {
    padding-top: 0;
    border-left: 2px solid #eee;
    padding-left: 32px;
  }
  .sidebar-section {
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .sidebar-section h4 {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
  }
  .rec-card {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .rec-card .rec-img {
    height: 140px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .rec-card .rec-img .img-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }
  .rec-card:hover .rec-img .img-placeholder { transform: scale(1.03); }
  .rec-card .rec-tag {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #B8432A;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .rec-card h5 {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1C1714;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .rec-card .card-meta {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #bbb;
  }
  .sidebar-ad {
    border: 1px dashed #ccc;
    border-radius: 4px;
    height: 250px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #bbb;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  /* ===== MORE ARTICLES (bottom) ===== */
  .more-articles {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 40px 60px;
  }
  .more-articles .section-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 32px 0 24px;
    border-top: 5px solid #6B4C3B;
  }
  .more-articles .section-header h3 {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .more-articles .section-header a {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #B8432A;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .more-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .more-card { cursor: pointer; }
  .more-card .more-img {
    height: 160px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .more-card .more-img .img-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }
  .more-card:hover .more-img .img-placeholder { transform: scale(1.03); }
  .more-card .more-tag {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #B8432A;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .more-card h4 {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1C1714;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .more-card .card-meta {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #bbb;
  }

  /* ===== NEWSLETTER + FOOTER (same as homepage) ===== */
  .newsletter-section {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 56px 40px;
    border-top: 2px solid #eee;
  }
  .newsletter-section h3 {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .newsletter-section p { font-size: 14px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .newsletter-section .coming-soon {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #ccc;
  }

  .footer {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
    padding: 48px 40px;
    border-top: 2px solid #eee;
  }
  .footer h5 {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .footer a {
    display: block;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #888;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .footer a:hover { color: #1C1714; }
  .footer-brand .logo-text {
    font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .footer-brand .tagline { font-size: 13px; color: #999; }
  .footer-bottom {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 16px 40px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #ccc;
    border-top: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .img-placeholder {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .article-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .article-sidebar { border-left: none; padding-left: 0; border-top: 2px solid #eee; padding-top: 32px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    /* Hero: 220px, flex-end layout matching mockup .ah */
    .article-hero { height: 220px; max-width: none; }
    .article-hero .hero-overlay {
      position: absolute; top: 0; transform: none;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-end;
    }
    .hero-overlay .breadcrumb { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.09em; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .hero-overlay .pillar-tag {
      display: inline-block; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.11em;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.11); padding: 3px 7px; border-radius: 2px; margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .hero-overlay h1 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 3px; max-width: none; }
    .hero-overlay .subtitle {
      font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; font-style: italic;
      font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); max-width: none; line-height: 1.4;
    }

    /* Meta bar: matches mockup .am */
    .article-meta-bar {
      max-width: none; padding: 11px 18px; border-bottom-width: 1px;
      flex-direction: row; align-items: center; gap: 0; justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .meta-left { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0; text-transform: none; color: #888; }
